+   - Show read-only markers in ls output
+
+2. **Update flowcharts if needed:**
+   - Add read-only indicator in diagrams
+
+3. **Add FAQ entry:**
+   - "Why is SESSION.md read-only?"
+   - "How do I track scope changes?"
